{"ts": 0.0, "op": "recall", "ids": ["mem_8d8b3a14", "mem_d0721663"], "query": "polyval timedelta64 fix", "meta": {"k": 5, "n": 2, "hits": [{"id": "mem_8d8b3a14", "content": "Add test cases to verify dataset_merge_method and dataset_update_method handle DataArray inputs correctly, confirming the fix produces identical results to the top-level merge function.", "score": 0.189304, "tokens": 46, "rank": 0, "timestamp": 1782516474.57524}, {"id": "mem_d0721663", "content": "When _Unsigned=\"true\" is found on signed byte data (i1), xarray converts it to unsigned bytes (u1), matching the netCDF convention. This existing behavior is preserved and not affected by the new fix.", "score": 0.175836, "tokens": 50, "rank": 1, "timestamp": 1782517243.57203}]}}
